   PLEASE NOTE.
   ------------
   All cheats have been found on a 1 meg chip Amiga,those who have 512kb chip
   & 512kb fast will find that some or all cheats will not work at all because
   the game will load the data differenty into this configuration.
    A new twist to maybe why it don't work maybe the fact the game loads the
   data differently under another kickstart-have a look at bubble bobble. 

