    Information on Gauntlet 2
    -------------------------

     About Transferability & Reflective shot for both colors.
     --------------------------------------------------------
     You will have noticed that these 2 actions are on the same address,the
     following is what needs to be done to get one or more.

     At 8568(blue) & 8528(red) put the following numbers in to get the
     following combinations.

     08 = Reflective Shot
     10 = Transferabilty
     18 = Reflective Shot & Transferability
     40 = IT (You are (IT) to the monsters to chace)
     48 = IT & Reflective Shot
     58 = IT,Reflective shot & Transferability

     Note:-) Every 2 address Action(except Level) can have a Value no
     higher than E6 FF or the game crashes.

            If anyone can find the EXTRA fight,shot,armour etc addresses
     then please send them into me.


