    About Rolling Thunder
    ---------------------
    The Rolling thunder cheat was found by using the method mentioned in
    NOTE 1. of TIME CLOCKS above.
    In order to change the lives,bullets etc counters you need to place 
    30 to 39 numbers in. E.G if the bullets counter shows 125 you need to
    enter this as 31 32 35 in order for it to work,so the max you can have
    is 999 or 39 39 39.


