    Sim City V1.1
    -------------
    TO FIND MONEY
    -------------
    Use FS to search for CONSOLE.DEVICE
    There will only be one address,you will find money address like this

        CONSOLE.DEVICE 00 77 FF FF FF 
            ^       ^                \ put 77 ff ff ff in the second 
            \      /                   byte after the console.device as
     just pretend this is in hex       shown to get 2013 million dollars
     on the hex side of ACTION REPLAY  
     
     The Money Value moves around on every load,but it will never move
     from the CONSOLE.DEVICE as shown,also put no higher than shown value
     into the address or game will crash.

    Sim City V1.2 turbo
    -------------------
    TO FIND MONEY
    -------------
    Use FS to search for GIMME VERSION
    There will only be one address,you will find money address like this

          GIMME VERSION 00 00 77 FF FF FF 
            ^       ^                \ put 77 ff ff ff in the third 
            \      /                   byte after the GIMME VERSION as
     just pretend this is in hex       shown to get 2013 million dollars
     on the hex side of ACTION REPLAY  
     
     The Money Value moves around on every load,but it will never move
     from the GIMME VERSION as shown,also put no higher than shown value
     into the address or game will crash.


