    Supremacy the ULTIMATE HACK FILE
    --------------------------------
                    OVER 200 ADDRESSES FOUND
                    ------------------------
  After 2 days of searching this great game I came up with the following. 

  Picking the first dude "WOTOK".
  The grid below is how the star system is mapped out when you go
  into the ship movement section of the game. STARBASE below and
  ENEMYBASE above. The best way to win this round is to boost up
  everything on Starbase as such.
  STARBASE:
	   Food = e380 + e381
       Minerals = e384 + e385
	   Fuel = e386 + e387
	 Energy = e388 + e389
	  Money = e38b Millions
		= e38c thousands
		= e38d hundreds
  |--------------|---------------|---------------|---------------|
  |  ENEMYBASE   |      	 |      	 |      	 |
  |--------------|---------------|---------------|---------------|
  |      ^       |      	 |      	 |      	 |
  |--------------|---------------|---------------|---------------|
  |      ^       |      	 |      	 |      	 |
  |--------------|---------------|---------------|---------------|
  |      ^       |      	 |      	 |      	 |
  |--------------|---------------|---------------|---------------|
  |      ^       |      	 |      	 |      	 |
