  |   PLANET 1   |      	 |      	 |      	 |
  |--------------|---------------|---------------|---------------|
  |   STARBASE   |      	 |      	 |      	 |
  |--------------|---------------|---------------|---------------|
  When you first go into the Action Replay,the screen will go black
  for a little while,from then on it will load normally unless you
  reset the machine.The first thing to do is buy a troop carrier
  then change the food etc addresses including the money values,with
  the food etc around 99 FF is a good number,for the money just FF
  all 3 for over 16 million dollars.Next go into the Platoon section
  and create 4 good Platoons using best armour and weopons,let them
  train to 5 star Generals.Load them in the carrier and speed off to
  the ENEMYBASE,land them on the planet and using the addresses
  below for the Platoons,alter your platoons to become invincible
  against the enemy and in a couple of minutes you have won.

