  Well I went back into the game and decided to look for some other
  hacks and this is what I found.

  DAY AND YEAR:
  -------------
  You will find the day address at e413,there is only 64 days in a
  year.The year address is e414 + e415.

  Next I tried to find the fuel address for all the ships,I did find
  it but it would have been hard to tell you where cos I wouldn't
  know how your ships are placed on the grid,so I went one step further.
  When you reach the year 2040 all your ships get nuclear drives,so
  that is what I found.

  B-29 BATTLE CRUISER
  -------------------
  ece0 + ece1      FF both addresses for nuclear drives.

  CARGO STORE/CARRIER
  -------------------
  eda0 + eda1      FF both addresses for nuclear drives.

  CORE-MINING STATION
  -------------------
  edc0 + edc1      FF both addresses for nuclear drives.

  HORTICULTURAL STATION
  ---------------------
  edf0 + edf1      FF both addresses for nuclear drives.

  For those of you who are interested in finding the fuel then go to
  e654,this is the top of the ship list.You will allways find
  the fuel at the start of the next craft in the list-E.G

  42 41 54 54 4c 45 2e 2e 31 ff 00 00 0e 50 00 00 BATTLE..1....P..
  00 00 00 00 00 15 00 00 00 00 00 00 dc 4e 01 00 .............n..
  02 18 00 00 00 00 01 90 41 54 4d 4f 53 2e 2e 2e ........ATMOS...
		    |  |  |     			  |
		    |  |  --------------------------------|
		    |  |				  |
		    FUEL			  SECOND SHIP
		FOR BATTLE..1


