          Over 200 items to be found,the bytes that have a X after them
          mean that there is no item attached to that byte.If you happen
          to find a hidden item anywhere then send me a line.
          
          A couple of hints when putting items in the back pack.
          It is possible to wear more than 1 piece of armour,you can if
          you like wear 12 pieces of armour,EQUIP the items in the Action
          Replay and go back into the game,if you are wearing 4 pieces of
          armour then your AC will be 4 times as great,you will only lose
          this if you UNEQUIP and then EQUIP a piece of armour as the game
          will reset all the other armours.
          It is allso possible for a magic user to wear the the best armour
          so long as you don't try to EQUIP other armour in the game.

